Margaret Adetutu Adeoye (amụrụ n'abalị iri abụọ na abụọ n'ọnwa Eprelụ n'afọ 1985) bụ onye na-eme egwuregwu na-eme asọmpi na mita 200. Ọ nọchitere anya Great Britain na London 2012.

E nwetara ihe kacha mma ya n'oge ahụ maka 200m na 6 Ọgọstụ 2012 mgbe ọ gbara ọsọ na 22.94s, na-enye ya ohere na Olympic 200m Semi-Finals. Ọ mechara nke asaa na Semi-Final, ọ nweghịkwa ọganihu na ṅgwụcha
N'afọ 2013, o jisiri ike melite ihe kacha mma ya ruo 22.88.
